      <description>&lt;p&gt;I went to Chile with a wining sensation in my mind. And I won.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Best poster award BIOMAT 2011 - Chile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://widgets.figshare.com/articles/91381/embed?show_title=1&#34; width=&#34;568&#34; height=&#34;351&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;p&gt;But I wasn&amp;rsquo;t there when it was announced because I went to the house of
Pablo Neruda and bought some presents for my family, anyway it was a
magic afternoon.&lt;/p&gt;
